  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nOn IPV6 enabled machines tests involving ganache fork fails because localhost resolves to `::1` instead of `127.0.0.1` which is the default ganache listening address.\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nUnstable cfa518a\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nTests fail with:\r\n\r\n```\r\nfailures:\r\n\r\n---- fallbacks::test_fallback_when_offline stdout ----\r\nthread 'fallbacks::test_fallback_when_offline' panicked at 'should start eth1 environment: \"Timed out waiting for ganache to start. Is ganache installed?\"', beacon_node/eth1/tests/test.rs:889:18\r\nnote: run with `RUST_BACKTRACE=1` environment variable to display a backtrace\r\n\r\n---- fallbacks::test_fallback_when_node_far_behind stdout ----\r\nthread 'fallbacks::test_fallback_when_node_far_behind' panicked at 'should start eth1 environment: \"Timed out waiting for ganache to start. Is ganache installed?\"', beacon_node/eth1/tests/test.rs:1031:18\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nTests should pass\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nChange the ganache fork endpoint hostname from `localhost` to `127.0.0.1` to match the ganache default listening address.\r\nWill provide PR for the change.\r\n",
